Had no idea that sh!t Kobe called himself had to do with the rape case. Kinda disgusts me. A 19 year girl was taken advantage of by someone with power. Then the case gets "forgotten" because well he is Kobe. Then he goes and does all these things to help the community. Guilty conscience much. Disgusting.


With the legal troubles behind him, Bryant created an alter ego, calling himself “Black Mamba” — after Africa’s deadliest snake, which figured in the 2003 movie “Kill Bill.”

“The whole process for me was trying to figure out how to cope with this,” Bryant told The Washington Post in 2018. “I wasn’t going to be passive and let this thing just swallow me up.”

Eventually there were Mamba shoes, a Mamba Sports Academy and the nickname “Mambacita” for Gianna, the second-born of the four daughters Bryant shared with his wife, Vanessa.


from https://www.nytimes.com/2020/01/27/sports/basketball/kobe-bryant-rape-case.html

Ara Zobayan🙏🏾 John and Keri and Alyssa Altobelli🙏🏾Sarah and Payton Chester🙏🏾 and Christina Mauser🙏🏾 #theirlivesmatterTOO

May their families have more love and support than they could’ve ever received publicly!!!
My most sincere condolences!!! 🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾🙏🏾
